OSIRIS / O.M.A.-C.O.R.E. CLI Commands
======================================

python -m core.cli.main run              # Ciclo completo: collect + process + telegram
python -m core.cli.main collect          # Solo recolectar eventos (usando WorldMonitorV2 con TODOS los collectors)
python -m core.cli.main process          # Solo procesar eventos pendientes
python -m core.cli.main council          # OSIRIS Agent Council (News + Macro agents → consensus → MetaCouncil)
python -m core.cli.main council --limit 100  # Council con mas eventos
python -m core.cli.main watch            # Monitoreo continuo (default 300s)
python -m core.cli.main watch --interval 60  # Cada 60 segundos
python -m core.cli.main status           # Ver estadisticas del sistema
python -m core.cli.main opportunities    # Ver oportunidades activas
python -m core.cli.main events --hours 24 --limit 50   # Ver eventos recientes
python -m core.cli.main export --format json   # Exportar a JSON
python -m core.cli.main export --format csv    # Exportar a CSV

OSIRIS Structure
================
core/schemas/agent_schema.py     # ACP: AgentOpinion, CouncilDecision, AgentRole, CouncilTier, Recommendation
core/event_bus/bus.py            # EventBus: pub/sub message bus with history
core/council/council.py          # AgentCouncil: consensus engine
core/council/meta_council.py     # MetaCouncil: cross-profile comparison
core/agents/news_agent.py        # NewsAgent: structured news analysis → AgentOpinion
core/agents/macro_agent.py       # MacroAgent: structured macro analysis → AgentOpinion
core/collectors/world_monitor_v2.py  # WorldMonitorV2: unified collector orchestrator (7 collectors)
core/profiles/models.py          # UserProfile, ProfileRegistry, Trader/Entrepreneur/Creator prefs
core/memory/memory.py            # ShortTermMemory, LongTermMemory, MemoryStore
core/config/config.py            # OSIRISConfig: centralized env-based config
